      <title>०२५ दिग्विजयाय प्रस्थानम्</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/mahAbhAratam/vyAsaH/goraxapura-pAThaH/hindy-anuvAdaH/02_sabhAparva/05_digvijayaparva/025_digvijayAya_prasthAnam/</link>
