    <item>
      <title>०३० प्राग्विजयः</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/mahAbhAratam/vyAsaH/goraxapura-pAThaH/hindy-anuvAdaH/02_sabhAparva/05_digvijayaparva/030_prAgvijayaH/</link>
